Iată cum ar trebui să fie query-ul corect:

```
let searchParam = "{SearchText}";
let tableName = "{TableName}";
table(tableName)
| where * has searchParam
| extend SearchValue = searchParam
| summarize count() by SearchValue
```

Sau alternativ, puteți folosi acest format:

```
let searchParam = "{SearchText}";
let tableName = "{TableName}";
search in (tableName) searchParam
| extend SearchValue = searchParam
| summarize count() by SearchValue
```